title.rendered: Tiddox 1000 sheet 3-Ply Blue Paper Roll Wipes

content.rendered:
Tiddox 1000 sheet 3-Ply Blue Paper Roll Wipes

  • 3-plys of glued and embossed paper for added absorbency, tear-resistance and wet strength
  • Multipurpose, disposable paper towels
  • Replace workshop rags with these grease and oil absorbent wipers to clean hands and tools
  • Ideal for low lint polishing of glass, sensitive equipment etc
  • Hospitality and Medical single-use wipers
  • Economical, Cost-Effective, European Quality
  • 350m x 1000 perforated sheets (36.5cm width)
